            "title": "Rivian Planning Door Redesign to Address Safety Concerns",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><div class=\"akcelo-wrapper akcelo-video media--169\" style=\"width:100%\"><div class=\"border:solid 1px #C0C0C0\" id=\"Zonebourse_Article_Video\" video-id=\"k28DBv0RIBlcGUDXWn6\"><div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta content=\"Rivian Planning Door Redesign to Address Safety Concerns\" itemprop=\"name\"/><meta content=\"Rivian (RIVN) is reworking a key element of the vehicle doors for its next-generation SUV after employees and customers raised concerns over potential safety issues with the current design. Ed Ludlow reports on Bloomberg Television.\n\" itemprop=\"description\"/><meta content=\"2025-10-03T17:37:05+02:00\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/><meta content=\"/images/mtnewswires/A3469915.png\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/><meta content=\"https://geo.dailymotion.com/player/x80uo.html?video=k28DBv0RIBlcGUDXWn6\" itemprop=\"embedUrl\"/></div></div></div>\n               Rivian (RIVN) is reworking a key element of the vehicle doors for its next-generation SUV after employees and customers raised concerns over potential safety issues with the current design. Ed Ludlow reports on Bloomberg Television.<p><span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTpvkfAwLuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'mtnewswires', '51254930');\">Bloomberg videos</span>, provided by MT Newswires</p></div>",
